OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fstart to the evening with a chance of
OL,7,Fsome light rain or showers along the
OL,8,Fnorth Norfolk coast. The cloud will
OL,9,Fbreak overnight inland but linger
OL,10,Faround the coasts. Ground frost
OL,11,Fpatches possible in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FSunny intervals and partly
OL,14,Fcloudy skies during the morning.
OL,15,FCloudier with occasional heavy showers
OL,16,Flater in the afternoon and evening,
OL,17,Fwith a chance of thunder. Cloudy
OL,18,Fovernight. Temperatures around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
